Sooooo let's see.. Since my last update, I've been going to gym like for a billion hours a day.  Adee has been gone for FAR TOO LONG! AHHHHH I miss the girl! hehe but she comes back soon so YAY. and I'm going to get her a pretty bday/grad present! =)

I kinda want the year to start because I'm anxious to leave for college. haha I talked to the Gymnastics coach from Cornell today. She called me and I was like OMG! I'm excited cause she sounds sorta interested and really nice. Anyway, I'm not getting my hopes up just yet or anything I'm just excited to start and finish this process. haha.

It almost feels like summer is over. I don't probably when Adee (and shelly for like a week) get back and the people who are still here get together, it'll be more like summer. I've spent the last like 10 nights with Kerri, since her parents have been in Europe. We had a lot of fun. =) Anyways, I am pretty bored and I just thought that I would post on lj since it's been like forever since. Mm Hmm 

My Amandita is away in Orroville... having fun in the sun. God damn her! not really because i miss her!!! haha I can't wait to go to Hawaii though, that is going to be SO FUN! AH! haha her big sis is turning 21 so partay.. I get to fly to Maui with her and i'm deathly afraid of flying. maybe she'll hook me up. hahah doubtful. hehe whatever. It's 1:30 and i have a bit of homework to do that's due Monday. Of course of COURSE. who the hell does NOT leave it til the last day, i mean HONESTLY. Haha i will pull thru. please help encourage me because i need a lot of it. Becaues yea i might break down and just give up!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! AHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH I'm reading the BIBLE. ahh... JOB.. haha not like the work.... like jobE. ha Yess. Don't ask about the user picture. I had to like totally show you that im part black ;) haha. Thats defnitely sorta Pat's line. But hey, im going to use it bitch. Well Yeah . I'm sad. I loved this winter break. It felt WAY long but WAY short at the same time. Just... how is that possible. Many memories made. Thanks guys I love you all. And i miss you mother fuckers who left already. Pej. You left Sunday. Come back in May for me please. K thanks =(. Pat you left tonight and it was sad saying goodbye yet AGAIN. sigh. Shelly tho, well shell came back tonigh and she stopped by for a minute and said hello. I will see her tomorrow. You can't go back i won't let you. Im SO not ready to start the whole school schedule thing again. Gr. Like not at ALL! And next new years I WANT TO BE ABLE TO DO SOMETHING! GRRRR but thats okay, its kinda really amusing watching drunk people. But when there are like thousands of bottles of alcohol within ur reach, really good junk food, you kinda forget how amusing it is and just want to cry. Then its like you get a call from another friend who isn't there with u and he's totally hammered too.. just fuck man. Happy 2005. And I don't have a resolution. Actually, I have a goal that I want achieved. Actually I have like 5. Maybe Ill tell you one day. Yesh. Yes. M-oh yes. Blah now I'm just saying nothing. But yeah. Next year at this time its going to be like 2359948579348793487 times worse. Cause I have my girlfriends who won't be here. because yeah. PLUS the ones who are already gone THIS year. FUCK. UGH. Just yeah. Id like to jump ahead 2 years from this very moment...sorta.. sorta not really tho. That's cool. So Im going to go now. This is one of the most journal-ish types of entries I've done in a while. And if you don't like any of it, well...well you can fuck off because this is my journal and yeah dude. YEA haha. Wow. I guess its time for me to go back to reading the bible. Man, i wish i went to church this Christmas. I do feel bad Jesus, I promis! haha look at me go. I love you all. And I hope all who drank themselves silly last night have recovered and no evidence of any of it was found. haha 

Peace the fuck out. 
 Brett

So here I am... chillin... at home... by myself...without a car... supposed to be at gym but my dad decided to take the car with all confidence that i start gym at 4. Right. let's try 10. So i walk outside with all my stuff in my hand expecting to find my silver beauty and there's nothing. so im slighty perplexed as to what is going on..while looking like an absolute idiot haha. yay. so now im here stuck for three house until i have a car. what the hell am i going to do. even the soap operas i like don't start until 2. haha yeah dude. I'm annoyed. but oh well. I guess I was meant to update my livejournal right this second. Yeah. So my birthday was the other day. That was cool and i got some really nice things. some you can see. and some you cannot =) I got a shirt from my mommy, a juicy jacket from kerri, a shirt and an awesome picture frame/collage from adee

 and i got a gift certificate from pat.. and some other stuff from him. haha which won't be mentioned. I had a lot of fun that night. My friends are home. that's exciting. Um i have a pretty christmas tree..... Ummmmmmmmmm my cats are cute and i want Christmas but i don't really because i always hate the day after Christmas. It's the most depressing day of the year. and yeah... it's just going to be really sad this year i can feel it.. blah. and shelly is sick and i hope she feels better because i love her. and yes. im SO ready to go to gym now. but its still only 10:40.. haha GREAT!
